  "texts": [
    "b Difference in rank overlap between fingerprints when comparing the values obtained on the COCONUT and Drug Repurposing Hub datasets.",
    "Positive overlaps mean that a given fingerprint pair has a higher overlap on natural products than on drug-like compounds.",
    "Asterisks denote significance (α=0.05) according to a one-sample Mann Whitney U test with Benjamini Hochberg correction.",
    "Raw p-values are available on the Github repository of this article.Figure S4.",
    "Significance of the Random Forest performance differences between fingerprint pairs across all datasets, according to a 2-tailed Wilcoxon test with the Benjamini-Hochberg correction."
